emuInput.TitMainTitle: George Auld wearing double breasted pinstriped suit, and Billy Eckstine, standing in Loendi Club, for reception in honor of Lena Horne
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 21, 1944, p. 13, reads: "GEORGE AULD, who has supported Lena with his band on several engagements was on hand ... and he and Eckstine compare notes on their rapid rise in music world. - Staff Photos by Harris."
